<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Counselor Invitation</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #1F2937;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #F3F4F6;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            border-radius: 16px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #7C3AED, #F97316);
            color: white;
            padding: 32px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 32px 24px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            background-color: #7C3AED;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 9999px;
            margin: 24px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }
        .button:hover {
            background-color: #6D28D9;
        }
        .link {
            background-color: #F3F4F6;
            padding: 12px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            word-break: break-all;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #4B5563;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 24px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #6B7280;
            background-color: #F9FAFB;
            border-top: 1px solid #E5E7EB;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Welcome to MiCounselor</h1>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hello,</p>
            
            <p>You've been invited to join MiCounselor as a counselor. We're excited to have you join our platform dedicated to healing connections and rebuilding bonds.</p>
            
            <p>Complete your registration and set up your counselor profile here:</p>
            
            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="<%= registrationLink %>" class="button">Complete Registration</a>
            </div>
            
            <p>Alternative link:</p>
            <div class="link"><%= registrationLink %></div>
            
            <p>This registration link is unique to you and will expire for security purposes. Contact our admin team if you need a new link.</p>
            
            <p>Best regards,<br>The MiCounselor Team</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>This is an automated message, please do not reply.</p>
            <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> MiCounselor. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>